_sText:
This is another map I remade from Halo.
So grab your shoT Guns (NOT SHOTTYS)
because the mind bending, tele confusing map is now on CS.

-Buyzones
-40 spawn points (I recommend 16~28 players when playing.)

For those of you who haven't played this map in halo, it's basically 8 rooms that link to others.
There are many paths to go through (not just one or two) this can be both an advantage and disadvantage for you. You might end up behind a group of enemies and you can mow them down but the same can happen to you so always watch your back!

Ps. There's a hidden banana in this map but you won't find it. ;)
